simple sincerity of the deluded housewife and ned bellamy is 
positively creepy as the looney deacon 
but a smirkiness and condescension pervade the proceedings 
whats more the play cant compete with the real thing jim and 
tammy bakker jimmy swaggart ollie north and all the rest of the 
people carnage attempts to harpoon are much more theatrical 
and funnier in real life than anything simon and robbins have put 
on stage 
